creator: Henry Wadsworth Longfellow
description:
LibriVox volunteers bring you 11 recordings of The Devil's Bridge by Henry Wadsworth Longfellow. This was the Fortnightly Poetry project for September 8, 2013. Read in English by Algy Pug; asterix; Claudia Salto; Kalif Storch; David Lawrence; Garth Burton; Jannie Meisberger; Julia Niedermaier; Larry Greene; Leonard Wilson; Michael Long. Taken from Poems of Places: An Anthology in 31 Volumes, Switzerland and Austria: Vol. XVI, edited by Henry Wadsworth Longfellow. (Summary by David Lawrence) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

M4B Format Available
